\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪又係咩818之後失民氣，完全無用之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但講呢d否定和理非既人完全蠢到忽略左818重點向來都唔係要林鄭跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係人都知和平對呢個政府無用啦屌，當人呢兩個月訓左咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n818重點從來都係呢三個:<br />\n1. 和理非沒有退場，五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n2. 重新為勇武行動授權，放核彈都不割<br />\n3. 為國際文宣製造話題，畫面<br />\n<br />\n所以咪係到懶醒話和理非無用了<br />\n撚唔知咩，和理非而家只係凝聚民意同幫各路抗爭活動上子彈。"},{"pid":"1ba16efbced61de0fba88e17a82e1647eeaf2ba3","tid":1494941,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:52:24.000Z","msg":"啊媽係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e01e3a2bd2d84ec9b216af5879d2235a011f9f","tid":1494941,"uid":264281,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:52:53.000Z","msg":"岩 睇下烏克蘭班後生仔依家點<br />\n被清算 通緝<br />\n成個國家仲黑暗 <br />\n係輸在班後生在位期間冇整死班老人"},{"pid":"9e5fb3bd607c12be14a24012e4529954ad4b6382","tid":1494941,"uid":249883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:53:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad2ec49ad92f4dddb77359f370ac9442c5ab08d1","tid":1494941,"uid":266736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:55:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3600ebdc957b30a6ac7e35412e5cf256e117df6","tid":1494941,"uid":254450,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b2eb1583195df4358e73090ef846d471396993ff","tid":1494941,"uid":173814,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:51:08.000Z","msg":"呢d扮智者分化和理非既post連登個個鐘都有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪又係咩818之後失民氣，完全無用之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但講呢d否定和理非既人完全蠢到忽略左818重點向來都唔係要林鄭跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係人都知和平對呢個政府無用啦屌，當人呢兩個月訓左咩<img src=\"/assets/